Insider Activity


Individual




Derek J. Kerr



Mr. Derek J. Kerr is Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President at American Airlines Group, Inc. and Chief Financial Officer, CAO & Executive VP at American Airlines, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Phoenix Zoo, Fiesta Bowl, University of Michigan Alumni Association, and Dallas Regional Chamber of Commerce.
Mr. Kerr was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by US Airways Group, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by US Airways, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by America West Holdings Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by America West Airlines, Inc., Control Engineer-B2 Division by Northrop Grumman Systems Corp., and a Principal by Northwest Airlines, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Michigan and an MBA from the University of Michigan.



